m_szDocSumamry: Tesla Model X & Model 3 On Schedule Originally published on EV Obsession . The delivery schedule for Tesla’s Model X SUV is still on track, going by the company’s most recent filing with the SEC (on April 23) — which reported that both the Alpha and Beta prototypes of the electric SUV had been completed. Following on the completion of those two prototypes, all that’s left now is the completion of the production version of the Model X — which is still (tentatively) due for release this September.
